12:
A crude iron great sword that,
despite its mass-produced
quality, packs quite a punch.

A great sword of fine steel,
with improved durability and
power for more demanding hunts.

A lavish great sword of rare
steel able to split even the
hardest of shells with ease.

The Nergigante scales on this
great sword continually regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.

Forged from Nergigante parts,

New forging techniques have been
used to give this iron great sword
a thunder element coating.

Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and thunder

New forging techniques have been
used to imbue this iron great sword
with the ice element.

Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and ice element

Wrapped in supple Jagras hide,

Throw some Kushala Daora bits

A Kulve Taroth great sword that

research purposes.

A Tigrex great sword. One

A blade housing the power of

One swing of this Raging

A dragon element great sword
hewn from bone, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.

All who wield this Shara Ishvalda

The heat within this Zorah

Wrapped in thunderous Rajang

this Brute Tigrex great sword,

Bestowed upon guild knights with

A great sword made from Safi'jiiva
